At this time only one mailing list exists (for any discusion related
to vq project), patches can be send directly to paweln@iidea.pl.

to subscribe:
send a letter to vq-request@cc.edu.pl with "subscribe" in a body

to unsubscribe:
send a letter to vq-request@cc.edu.pl with "unsubscribe" in a body

to get help:
send a letter to vq-request@cc.edu.pl with "help" in a body

to send a letter on a list:
send a letter to vq@cc.edu.pl, you need to be subscribed
